    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“天启”时刻临近，这一次... ...你为自己而战!</h2><strong>「天启派对」</strong>有别于前作「瘟疫清零计划」<br>这次你将更加深入这场惊心动魄的战斗，故事也逐渐变得不可思议！穿越？末日？阴谋？你将面对更多未知的挑战... ...但它依然是我们喜爱的RogueLike+割草的组合，并且你将可以与你的朋友一起联机面对这场浩劫（当然也可以独自面对）！<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ■ 全新模式，无限地牢 ■ </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/22011a9f573505b620411217b2c1cb0d.avif?t=1748419582\" width=606 height=196 /></span><br>在新模式里，你会遭到怪物一波又一波的猛烈进攻<br>除了常规的天赋升级外，还能从商店购买赐福、武器、锻造、天赋标签包、消耗品、甚至是下注等！<br>在这里，你没有成长的上限，数值将无限膨胀！<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ■ 既有趣又有深度的构筑 ■ </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/530609bf0e222fe256c9599d691f3118.poster.avif?t=1748419582\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/530609bf0e222fe256c9599d691f3118.webm?t=1748419582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>天赋总数突破570个！并且大部分都是改变战局的机制类天赋</strong><br>另外还有：<br>- 超过60种不同手感的武器类型！<br>- 20+个充满想象力的神技大招！（包括各类法术巫术、驾驶车辆、召唤轰炸机、化身山岭巨人、甚至使用谜之二向箔等）<br>- 千奇百怪的召唤物，协助你战斗！<br><strong>提供了多维度的构筑可能性！</strong>丰富程度前所未有! 每次尝试，都能把你想象中的流派变成现实！<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ■ 今夜一起加入猎杀派对吗? ■ </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/d62f8f340f79c5902d5555f5c4edb75a.poster.avif?t=1748419582\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/d62f8f340f79c5902d5555f5c4edb75a.webm?t=1748419582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>海量的尸潮，爽快的割草，怎能一人独享？<br>想象一下和你的朋友一起遨游在丧尸海洋里的快乐!<br>叫上他(她)们，尝试一起在末日活下去吧！（最多支持3人噢）<br><strong>当然,我们必须友善的提醒您,并不排斥“友尽”的可能：）</strong><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ■ 一墙的可用角色，量大管饱 ■ </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/354fe81ae4174ab432fdec6e86fe552f.poster.avif?t=1748419582\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/354fe81ae4174ab432fdec6e86fe552f.webm?t=1748419582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>40个角色，每人有3个不同的被动技能，在这里你可以选择成为<br>- 骑龙飞翔的龙母<br>- 可以幻化成狼的驯兽师<br>- 强迫尸群跳舞的电子乐手<br>- 每次升级都要赌上一把的性感荷官<br>- 甚至是把游戏直接变成音游的吟游诗人（逐渐离谱）<br><strong>上百个玩法各异的角色技能</strong>，让你每次开局都有满满的新鲜感<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ■ 多种游玩模式，不止割草 ■ </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/1e211c770f5162079d250623b00c44c4.poster.avif?t=1748419582\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/1e211c770f5162079d250623b00c44c4.webm?t=1748419582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>除了收割尸潮的清零模式外，你还可以在<strong>新模式“无限地牢”</strong>里爬塔冲层，挑战人类极限，<br>也可以在超高难度的<strong>“地狱模式”</strong>里完成竞速通关，冲击<strong>排行榜</strong>！！<br>在这里，各种硬核的需求都能得到满足。。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ■ 你将与整个地狱为敌 ■ </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/b917146ce4a7d0b035000c5b96ccbcc1.poster.avif?t=1748419582\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/b917146ce4a7d0b035000c5b96ccbcc1.webm?t=1748419582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>每场战斗都会遭遇随机Boss，<br>只有搭配得当的构筑，才能让你击败他们！<br>成功到达关底后，迎接你的将会是地狱的领主 - 撒旦！<strong>做好打一场恶战的准备吧，朋友！</strong><br><br>...<br><br><strong>“既然末日已来，加入我们，进行最后的狂欢吧！”</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351560/extras/ad2777894e608c96ac7a6fd604791f70.avif?t=1748419582\" width=606 height=196 /></span>",
